<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Classic Shell 4.3.1 is released [Aug 12th 2017]]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7807&amp;p=33649#p33649"><![CDATA[
Here is the detailed change log for Classic Shell 4.3.1:<br /><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">New features in Classic Shell 4.3.1:</span><br />● New command in the Backup button of the Settings window to clear the icon cache without restarting the menu<br />● Alt+Enter keyboard shortcut to open Properties of Start menu items and jumplist items<br /><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">Other minor changes and fixes in Classic Shell 4.3.1:<br /></span><br />● Fixed an issue with the Start button in some cases appearing in fullscreen programs and games.<br />● Added a confirmation dialog when you cancel the changes made in Settings<br />● The Settings window remembers its maximized state<br />● Fixed the bug where &lt;No Skin&gt; was missing icons<br />● Fixed a crash where the search would crash if the programs tree in Windows 7 style was disabled<br />● Fixed the broken taskbar texture for Windows 10 Creators Update<br />● Fixed a bug where sometimes the jumplist items wouldn't work<br />● Fixed the broken Start Screen shortcut for Windows 8<br />● Fixed a bug where the taskbar color was wrong on Windows 8 if only the opacity was customized<br />● Fixed a crash when dragging an item from a submenu or a jumplist to the search box to pin it<br />● Fixed a crash with Windows 10 Creators Update when pinning UWP apps from search results<br />● Updated code signing certificate for this version<br /><br />Previous release was <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6412" class="postlink"><strong>Classic Shell 4.3.0</strong></a>.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Sun Aug 13, 2017 12:35 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
