<title type="html"><![CDATA[Classic Shell 4.3.1 is released [Aug 12th 2017]]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7807&amp;p=33644#p33644"><![CDATA[
Classic Shell 4.3.1 was just released. Download it from here: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.classicshell.net">http://www.classicshell.net</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Here’s what’s new:<ul><li> Official support for the Creators Update version of Windows 10</li><li> Added a setting to clear icon cache</li><li> Multiple minor improvements and bugfixes</li></ul><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Sat Aug 12, 2017 5:41 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
